<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Mateo Amaya — Ciberseguridad</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #050a0e;
      --bg2: #0a1218;
      --green: #00ff9d;
      --green-dim: #00cc7a;
      --cyan: #00e5ff;
      --red: #ff3c5c;
      --text: #c8d8e0;
      --text-dim: #5a7a8a;
      --border: #0f2535;
      --card: #080f15;
      --mono: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      --sans: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: 16px;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      cursor: default;
    }

    /* SCANLINE OVERLAY */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 2px,
        rgba(0,255,157,0.012) 2px,
        rgba(0,255,157,0.012) 4px
      );
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9999;
    }

    /* NOISE TEXTURE */
    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9998;
      opacity: 0.4;
    }

    /* ===== NAVBAR ===== */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1rem 3rem;
      background: rgba(5,10,14,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      color: var(--green);
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .nav-logo span { color: var(--text-dim); }

    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    nav ul a {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      color: var(--text-dim);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: color 0.2s;
      position: relative;
    }

    nav ul a::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -4px; left: 0;
      width: 0; height: 1px;
      background: var(--green);
      transition: width 0.3s;
    }

    nav ul a:hover { color: var(--green); }
    nav ul a:hover::after { width: 100%; }

    /* ===== HERO ===== */
    #hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8rem 3rem 4rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-grid-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,255,157,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,255,157,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 80% at 50% 50%, black 30%, transparent 100%);
    }

    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20%; left: 55%;
      width: 600px; height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,255,157,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    .hero-tag {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      color: var(--green);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .hero-tag::before {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 24px; height: 1px;
      background: var(--green);
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 .accent { color: var(--green); }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }

    .hero-desc {
      color: var(--text-dim);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-btns {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.8rem;
      border: 1px solid;
      transition: all 0.25s;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--green);
      color: var(--bg);
      border-color: var(--green);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      border-color: var(--border);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      border-color: var(--green);
      color: var(--green);
    }

    /* STATUS TERMINAL */
    .status-bar {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 3rem; right: 3rem;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      text-align: right;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .status-bar .live { color: var(--green); }

    /* ===== SECTIONS ===== */
    section {
      padding: 6rem 3rem;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    .section-num {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      color: var(--green);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #fff;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .section-line {
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
    }


    /* CERT PREVIEW OVERLAY */
    #cert-overlay {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    #cert-overlay.visible {
      display: flex;
    }

    #cert-overlay-img {
      width: min(500px, 90vw);
      border: 2px solid var(--green);
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,255,157,0.3), 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.9);
      transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
      display: block;
    }

    #cert-overlay.visible #cert-overlay-img {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
    }

    .cert-card.has-link:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.5);
    }

    .cert-card.has-preview { cursor: zoom-in; }

    /* ===== SKILLS ===== */
    .skills-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .skill-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color 0.25s, transform 0.25s;
    }

    .skill-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 3px; height: 0;
      background: var(--green);
      transition: height 0.3s;
    }

    .skill-card:hover { border-color: rgba(0,255,157,0.3); transform: translateY(-3px); }
    .skill-card:hover::before { height: 100%; }

    .skill-icon {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .skill-name {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      color: var(--green);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }



    /* ===== CERTIFICATES ===== */
    .cert-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .cert-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.8rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }

    .cert-card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,255,157,0.04) 0%, transparent 60%);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }

    .cert-card:hover { border-color: rgba(0,255,157,0.4); transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .cert-card:hover::after { opacity: 1; }

    .cert-badge {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      background: rgba(0,255,157,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,157,0.2);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .cert-issuer {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: var(--green);
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .cert-name {
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .cert-desc {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .cert-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      color: var(--cyan);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.2);
      padding: 2px 8px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    /* ADD CERT CARD */
    .cert-add {
      border: 1px dashed var(--border);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      min-height: 180px;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }

    .cert-add:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }

    .cert-add .plus {
      font-size: 2rem;
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* ===== ABOUT ===== */
    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .about-text p {
      color: var(--text-dim);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .terminal-box {
      background: #020608;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .terminal-bar {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 10px; height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .dot-r { background: #ff5f56; }
    .dot-y { background: #ffbd2e; }
    .dot-g { background: #27c93f; }

    .t-line {
      color: var(--text-dim);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .t-line .prompt { color: var(--green); }
    .t-line .cmd { color: #fff; }
    .t-line .out { color: var(--cyan); }
    .t-line .comment { color: #3a5a6a; }

    /* ===== CONTACT ===== */
    .contact-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .contact-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.2rem 1.8rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      transition: all 0.25s;
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 200px;
    }

    .contact-link:hover {
      border-color: var(--green);
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .contact-link .icon { font-size: 1.3rem; }

    /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem 3rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--text-dim);
    }

    /* ===== ANIMATIONS ===== */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50%       { opacity: 0; }
    }

    .hero-content > * {
      animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both;
    }

    .hero-tag        { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .hero-content h1 { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
    .hero-subtitle   { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
    .hero-desc       { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    .hero-btns       { animation-delay: 0.6s; }

    .cursor {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 8px; height: 1em;
      background: var(--green);
      vertical-align: text-bottom;
      animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    }


    .tw-cursor {
      color: var(--green);
      animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    }


    /* CERT CARD SPLIT CLICK */
    .cert-card.has-preview { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }

    .cert-badge-btn {
      cursor: zoom-in;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      background: rgba(0,255,157,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,157,0.2);
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .cert-badge-btn:hover {
      background: rgba(0,255,157,0.18);
      border-color: var(--green);
    }

    .cert-body { position: relative; z-index: 2; cursor: pointer; }

    /* Image overlay inside card */
    .cert-inner-img {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: #000;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.25s;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    .cert-inner-img.show {
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: all;
    }
    .cert-inner-img img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }
    .cert-inner-img .close-btn {
      position: absolute;
      top: 8px; right: 10px;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--green);
      cursor: pointer;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--green);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .cert-inner-img .close-btn:hover { background: var(--green); color: #000; }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
      nav ul { gap: 1.2rem; }
      section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
      #hero { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
      .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .status-bar { display: none; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; text-align: center; }
    }

    /* ===== CUSTOM CURSOR ===== */
    * { cursor: none !important; }

    /* ===== PARTICLES ===== */
    #particles-canvas {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    #hero, nav, section, footer {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* ===== SCROLL REVEAL ===== */
    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(32px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
    }
    .reveal.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    .reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
    .reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
    .reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
    .reveal-delay-4 { transition-delay: 0.4s; }

    /* ===== GLITCH ===== */
    .glitch {
      position: relative;
    }
    .glitch::before,
    .glitch::after {
      content: attr(data-text);
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    .glitch::before {
      color: var(--cyan);
      clip-path: polygon(0 20%, 100% 20%, 100% 40%, 0 40%);
    }
    .glitch::after {
      color: var(--red);
      clip-path: polygon(0 60%, 100% 60%, 100% 80%, 0 80%);
    }
    .glitch.glitching::before {
      opacity: 0.8;
      animation: glitch-top 0.15s steps(2) forwards;
    }
    .glitch.glitching::after {
      opacity: 0.8;
      animation: glitch-bot 0.15s steps(2) forwards;
    }

    @keyframes glitch-top {
      0%   { transform: translate(-4px, -2px) skewX(-3deg); }
      33%  { transform: translate(4px, 2px) skewX(3deg); }
      66%  { transform: translate(-2px, 1px) skewX(-1deg); }
      100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
    }
    @keyframes glitch-bot {
      0%   { transform: translate(4px, 2px) skewX(3deg); }
      33%  { transform: translate(-4px, -2px) skewX(-3deg); }
      66%  { transform: translate(2px, -1px) skewX(1deg); }
      100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
    }


    /* ===== EASTER EGG: SUDO SU ===== */
    #sudo-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: #000;
      z-index: 999999;
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: var(--mono);
    }

    #sudo-overlay.active { display: flex; }

    #sudo-terminal {
      width: min(640px, 90vw);
      border: 1px solid var(--green);
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,255,157,0.3), 0 0 80px rgba(0,255,157,0.1);
    }

    .sudo-bar {
      background: #0a1a0f;
      padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--green);
    }

    .sudo-bar span {
      color: var(--green);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    #sudo-body {
      background: #000;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      min-height: 260px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      line-height: 2;
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .sudo-line { overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; }
    .sudo-line.red   { color: #ff3c5c; }
    .sudo-line.cyan  { color: var(--cyan); }
    .sudo-line.white { color: #fff; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .sudo-line.dim   { color: var(--text-dim); }

    #sudo-close {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
      background: transparent;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    #sudo-close:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }

    .sudo-blink {
      animation: blink 0.6s step-end infinite;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- PARTICLES CANVAS -->
<canvas id="particles-canvas"></canvas>

<!-- CUSTOM CURSOR -->
<canvas id="cursor-canvas"></canvas>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo"><span id="typewriter"></span><span class="tw-cursor">_</span></div>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#sobre-mi">Sobre mí</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#certificados">Certs</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contacto">Contacto</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div id="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-tag">Ciberseguridad</div>
    <h1><span class="glitch" data-text="Mateo">Mateo</span><br><span class="accent glitch" data-text="Amaya">Amaya</span></h1>
    <div class="hero-subtitle">$ whoami — Ethical Hacker & Security Student</div>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      Estudiante de ciberseguridad apasionado por Linux, las redes y el hacking ético.
      Actualmente mejorando mis habilidades mediante prácticas de laboratorio y ejercicios prácticos.
    </p>
    <p class="hero-desc" style="font-size:0.92rem; margin-top:-0.8rem;">
      📚 Cursando <strong style="color:#fff;">Técnico Superior en Ciberseguridad</strong> en el
      <strong style="color:#fff;">Colegio Universitario IES</strong> — formándome con base técnica sólida
      en seguridad de sistemas, redes y análisis de vulnerabilidades.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#certificados" class="btn btn-primary">Ver certificados</a>
